{"tid":124810,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"精神有問題的臭貓","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T17:06:03.000Z","uid":62282,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5c6fd5eb24a05c0c7fd3cb5efe18e3aac095c4","tid":124810,"uid":62282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:38:23.000Z","msg":"介紹返我隻臭貓<br />\n<br />\n係異國短毛貓，正常應該乖乖地蠢蠢地，點知每次一睇獸醫打針，佢就會發晒癲。特別係探熱時，醫生一塞支探熱針去佢屎忽，佢就狂叫同咬人。醫生話從未見過一隻咁惡同性格咁強烈的異短，話可能係個腦有問題，建議我consult一下貓的腦科專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/103423_d75a005f70fae78f4cbb2d1e2ab58ea4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F103423_d75a005f70fae78f4cbb2d1e2ab58ea4.jpg&h=440e4e54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/orfYKq7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2ForfYKq7.jpg&h=9f491d24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/103424_d75a005f70fae78f4cbb2d1e2ab58ea4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F103424_d75a005f70fae78f4cbb2d1e2ab58ea4.jpg&h=b1fbb7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73B393f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73B393f.jpg&h=d91823e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/103425_1deb00aa852bead2f18230d0ee92afe7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F103425_1deb00aa852bead2f18230d0ee92afe7.jpg&h=f2ce1fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢無得醫架喇"},{"pid":"e7304d7f950862bc3bd268a4abcf1754782140e0","tid":124810,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:40:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80e