oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705d23c69fcfa2f0c15689811c5922930e1d8a9","tid":124810,"uid":9153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3b1313a635ae8441c79495a1019625a62bac4f","tid":124810,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AC5VLZr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAC5VLZr.jpg&h=1841b362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/210545_a22b07971b801f6575ca271346a99aa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F210545_a22b07971b801f6575ca271346a99aa1.jpg&h=817b6818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鬥癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967b911bbcde6688a9cd6e9691fe14e74c9201d1","tid":124810,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"睇緊異短諗住養<br />\n<br />\n想知道係咪要每日抹一次眼淚？？？<br />\n<br />\n早幾日上左間舖頭睇，有隻九個月大既流左一d深色既淚水<br />\n<br />\n睇落好似冇咩精神咁，點樣先知道佢係眼訓定有問題<br />\n<br />\n但係抱住佢個陣唔肯放手， 差d忍唔住即刻帶佢番屋企"},{"pid":"92b63daffe0a0c90519dcbcba7494723fe9ef681","tid":124810,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"唔係正常架咩<br />\n我兩隻貓晌屋企都好嗲人<br />\n睇獸醫對獸醫同姑娘勁惡<br />\n見番我又收晒火"},{"pid":"aa1e2b87033b702efdfec97f60259ac9c609a85a","tid":124810,"uid":27537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇緊異短諗住養<br />\n<br />\n想知道係咪要每日抹一次眼淚？？？<br />\n<br />\n早幾日上左間舖頭睇，有隻九個月大既流左一d深色既淚水<br />\n<br />\n睇落好似冇咩精神咁，點樣先知道佢係眼訓定有問題<br />\n<br />\n但係抱住佢個陣唔肯放手， 差d忍唔住即刻帶佢番屋企</blockquote><br />\n兩次差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyeXk13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyeXk13.jpg&h=3ffbdec3&s={SIZE}\" />今年12歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701a8a98ea68b1f53de34d00cb4aba90f428b2f3","tid":124810,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/004931_80e432101d8e1b784eda076bf30bbd2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F004931_80e432101d8e1b784eda076bf30bbd2c.jpg&h=25e858fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/004937_a9b6617cecd3dd5572dce74a973e63c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F004937_a9b6617cecd3dd5572dce74a973e63c9.jpg&h=3c010a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢平時正正常常，但有時上一秒正常，下一秒就著晒，癲咗係屋企亂跑，有次朋友帶左佢隻貓貓上黎我屋企，點知我隻臭貓就好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我唸佢唔適合交朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隻臭貓都會 一到咁上下鐘數就發癲<br />\n係咁跑係咁跳 仲係係床自己係到幻想有敵人去兇佢<br />\n<br />\n不過就算比佢攻擊到都唔痛😂"}]}